Deutsche Bahn Sees Acquisition Chances for Arriva, FTD Reports

-- B y   N i k l a s   M a g n u s s o n
-- 
2011-09-15T06:33:03Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-15/deutsche-bahn-sees-acquisition-chances-for-arriva-ftd-reports.html
Deutsche Bahn  AG sees acquisition
and growth opportunities in  Europe  for its Arriva unit, the
 Financial Times Deutschland  reported today, citing Ulrich Homburg, who heads Deutsche Bahn’s passenger transport division.  Arriva isn’t interested in buying  Spain ’s Avanza, which is
“totally overpriced” and isn’t in talks with the company,
Homburg told the newspaper.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Niklas Magnusson in Hamburg at 
 nmagnusson1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  